FORMULAS IN SPREADSHEET (google sheet)
# Basic calculations like sum, sub, mul and divide and little bit for math formulas
# Formula starts with "=" sign 
Cell refernce - coloumn letter and row number
range - one or more row/coloumn.

# By changing the values in observation, value in the formula will also update automatically.#
#  Formulas make it easy for data analysts to do powerful calculations automatically, which helps them analyze data more effectively.

Absolute referencing
 - Absolute referencing is marked by a dollar sign ($). For example, =$A$10 has absolute referencing for both the column and the row value
 
